<section id="space" class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12">
        <h2 class="title text-center" id="workshop_info">The Space</h2>
        <p>We have a new space!</p>

        <p>In July 2018, we moved into our new space on Albert St. We are now in the Tech School building, with entrance via the South-side of the building (up the stairs). For disabled access, there is a lift at the footpath on the South-East corner. It is secured, so just ping us on slack if you need us to let you in (if you can, gives us a day's warning that you will need it - it's fine if you don't, but this makes it easier to manage).</p>

        <p>Please come along and check us out at our next meetup, or any time we are open. <b>Right now</b>, for July 2018, access outside of hours is a little tricky (we are working on this as a priority). If you plan on visiting outside opening times, please just contact us with at least a day's warning and we can sort something out. Scroll up a little to checkout our opening times (or <a href="#timetable">click here</a>).</p>

        <p>Join the Ballarat Hackerspace to be part of our active and growing community. Casual members can use the space's equipment and facilities during opening hours. Full time members can get 24-7 access to the space (with committee approval).</p>

        <p>You are also welcome to join the <a href="/contact#slack">Slack</a>, or follow us on <a href="https://twitter.com/bHackerspace">Twitter</a> or <a href="https://plus.google.com/communities/106879016585907671427">Google+</a></p>

        <h3>Facilities</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Electronics area with soldering (wand and reflow), desoldering, scopes and meters</li>
          <li>3D printing</li>
          <li>Small scale CNC</li>
          <li>Internet access</li>
          <li>Projector/Presentation</li>
          <li>Kitchen</li>
          <li>(So much) room for activities!</li>
          <li>Equipment for use in the space (think keyboards, monitors, cables etc)</li>
          <li>Library of technical books</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Before visiting the space</h3>
